    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Not sure about what's the best solution, maybe an option for the `hits` widget would be good like you mentioned.\n\nHaving a way to remove refined facets when having no-results is - I think - a best practice in terms of UX, so I would advocate for having it in the default widgets one way or another.\n",
